    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture produced in Iran by the Medes culture from the rise of their state in the 7th century BCE to their defeat by the Achaemenid Cyrus the Great in 550 BCE.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000045119/Frankfort, Art and Architecture of the Ancient Orient (1996)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al estilo de arte y arquitectura producido en Irán por Medes desde la ascensión de su estado en el siglo VII a.C. a su derrota por el Aqueménida Cyrus el Grande en 550 a.C.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de stijl van de kunst en architectuur die in Iran werd vervaardigd door de Meden vanaf de opkomst van hun staat in de 7de eeuw v. Chr. tot aan hun omverwerping door de Achaemenische Cyrus de Grote in 550 n. Chr.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指自西元前七世紀至西元前550年間於伊朗發展的藝術與建築風格，此風格興起於米底人的建國，結束於阿契美尼德王朝居魯士大帝的征服入侵。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
